 March 5 , 1916 Sunday Reviell as per usual Hors exercis this morn then we had the day off , no mail no pay , so wrote letter in the afternoon . One of our plane left for Assuit where we are rumor to be go to , the Lovat Scout have gone also . Armour car have been make demonstr daili the nigger do n't half like it . Play card at night then did the next best thing turn in at 10 oclock . Our arab is still improv . March 6 , 1916 Monday 72 wks of soldier Reviell at 6.30 Clean out the old bus finish the water flume we have been make but owe to the belt continu jam we had to give it best . At 5 oclock I got order to go to Bahrasa , caught the train left Beni Mazar at 6.30 arriv at Bahrasa at 7.30 , had tea in the Officer mess left at 8 the lamp prove troublesom right from the jump when cross a canal it went out I found myself in a bursein crop got out made Beni Mazar at 9 , got as far as Kilnich when I broke a valv , put up for the night at a merchant place who gave me a splendid feed I turn in at 1.30 after fill in the night with music .
